'''草酸钪'''是钪的草酸盐，化学式为Sc<sub>2</sub>(C<sub>2</sub>O<sub>4</sub>)<sub>3</sub>，其六水合物可由[[氯化钪|氯化钪]]和过量[[草酸|草酸]]在稀溶液中于60 °C反应得到。<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Journal of the American Chemical Society|volume=73|issue=3|language=en|issn=0002-7863|date=1951-03|pages=1364–1364|doi=10.1021/ja01147a516|url=https://pubs.acs.org/doi/abs/10.1021/ja01147a516|title=The Chemistry of Scandium. III 1,2|accessdate=2020-10-12|author=Morton J. Klein, Peter M. Bernays}}</ref>六水合物和[[氨气|氨气]]反应，可以得到[Sc(NH<sub>3</sub>)<sub>6</sub>]<sub>2</sub>(C<sub>2</sub>O<sub>4</sub>)<sub>3</sub>。<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Journal of the Chemical Society (Resumed)|language=en|issn=0368-1769|date=1955|pages=255|doi=10.1039/jr9550000255|url=http://xlink.rsc.org/?DOI=jr9550000255|title=Scandium oxalate and its ammine complexes|accessdate=2020-10-12|author=R. C. Vickery}}</ref>

草酸钪高温下分解，生成[[氧化钪|氧化钪]]、[[一氧化碳|一氧化碳]]和[[二氧化碳|二氧化碳]]。<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Journal of Inorganic and Nuclear Chemistry|volume=26|issue=4|language=en|date=1964-04|pages=525–530|doi=10.1016/0022-1902(64)80284-0|url=https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/0022190264802840|title=The thermal decomposition of scandium formate and oxalate|accessdate=2020-10-12|author=E.L. Head, C.E. Holley}}</ref>

